## 1. Purpose

This readiness plan prepares {{ business_name }} for the anticipated requirements of **Tranche 2** of the **Privacy and Other Legislation Amendment (POLA) Act 2024**. While Tranche 1 introduced the statutory tort of serious invasion of privacy, children's privacy protections, and enhanced enforcement powers, Tranche 2 is expected to introduce **high-risk AI regulation**, **mandatory AI registers**, and **enhanced transparency obligations**. This plan identifies gaps between {{ business_name }}'s current posture and anticipated requirements, and provides an implementation timeline.

{% if tranche2_aware %}
{{ business_name }} has acknowledged awareness of Tranche 2. This plan formalises that awareness into concrete readiness actions.
{% else %}
**Note:** {{ business_name }} has not yet formally acknowledged Tranche 2 preparations. This plan should be reviewed and endorsed by senior leadership as a priority.
{% endif %}

