## 6. Enhanced Transparency Obligations

### 6.1 Anticipated Requirements

Tranche 2 is expected to require:

- **Notification at point of interaction** — individuals must know they are interacting with AI
- **Explanation of logic** — individuals must be able to understand how AI decisions are made
- **Right to human review** — individuals must be able to request human reconsideration of AI decisions
- **AI-generated content labelling** — AI-generated text, images, and media must be identified as such

